- 完整的 5 级事件链已注册：
    ADJUSTMENT_CREATED/UPDATED/DELETED → on_adjustment_changed → TRIAL_BALANCE_UPDATED
    MAPPING_CHANGED → on_mapping_changed → TRIAL_BALANCE_UPDATED
    DATA_IMPORTED → on_data_imported → TRIAL_BALANCE_UPDATED
    TRIAL_BALANCE_UPDATED → on_trial_balance_updated → REPORTS_UPDATED
    REPORTS_UPDATED → on_reports_updated → 附注增量更新
    WORKPAPER_SAVED → _on_workpaper_saved → 审定数比对

